Message: Social media is already filling up with misinformation about a Covid-19 vaccine, months or years before one even exists. "The anti-vaxxers have been practicing for this," writes Kevin Roose. "And I’m worried that they will be unusually effective."
We’ve been warning about this for 6 years...
Anti-vaxxers have gotten so effective at pushing misinformation that scientists are now concerned when a Covid-19 vaccine does come out many will simply refuse to take it.
Get Ready for a Vaccine Information War Social media is already filling up with misinformation about a Covid-19 vaccine, months or years before one even exists. Technology
